#
# Create the configuration by running the following command:
#
# sudo -u znc /usr/local/bin/znc --datadir=/var/lib/znc --makeconf
#
# After creating the configuration, the process is forked into the background.
# If you wont to use smf, you will need to stop the znc process and start it
# back again via smf:
#
# pkill znc
# scvadm enable znc
#
